onRegisterFailed = Mock()
onRegisterSuccess = Mock()
self.face.registerPrefix(Name('/test/register/callbacks'), None,
    onRegisterFailed, onRegisterSuccess)
while True:
    self.face.processEvents()
    time.sleep(0.01)
    if onRegisterSuccess.call_count > 0 or onRegisterFailed.call_count > 0:
        break
self.assertEqual(onRegisterSuccess.call_count, 1, 
    'Expected 1 onRegisterSuccess callback, got ' + str(onRegisterSuccess.
    call_count))
